         <abstract id="aspace_803e8f6eae9b9d31c107d5a4789f551e">The records consist of reports, score books, publications, and scrapbooks maintained primarily by the Department of Athletics documenting baseball at Yale.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <corpname rules="aacr" source="local">
               <part>Yale University. Dept. of Athletics</part>
